{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"StorageEstimate.quota","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate_78aa4ffd4dfacc8f94d5c05d150d36ac","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage_API\">Storage API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageManager\"><code>StorageManager</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>estimate()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persist\"><code>persist()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/persisted\"><code>persisted()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Storage に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/storage\"><code>Navigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerNavigator/storage\"><code>WorkerNavigator.storage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>安全なコンテキスト用:</strong> この機能は一部またはすべての<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">対応しているブラウザー</a>において、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">安全なコンテキスト</a> (HTTPS) でのみ利用できます。</p></div></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>StorageEstimate</code></a> ディクショナリの <strong><code>quota</code></strong> プロパティは、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>StorageManager.estimate()</code></a> を呼ぶことで得られる、オリジンやウェブアプリに割り当てられているストレージの量の控えめな概算値です。</span> より多くの利用可能なスペースがあるかもしれませんが、少なくなることはありません。この値は、フィンガープリンティング、つまり一見無害なプロパティの値を統合してデバイスを識別するための使用を防止するのに役立つ概算値です。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>quota</em> = <em>StorageEstimate</em>.quota;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<p>アプリで使用可能な合計ストレージ容量の概算値を指定する数値。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p>この例では、使用量の概算値を取得し、現在使用しているストレージ容量のパーセント値をユーザーに提示します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html_content","title":"HTML の内容","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  現在、使用可能なストレージの約 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>output</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>percent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>output</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>% を使用しています。\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>label</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript_content","title":"JavaScript の内容","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>storage<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">estimate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">estimate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"percent\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value <span class=\"token operator\">=</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>estimate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>usage <span class=\"token operator\">/</span> estimate<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>quota <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toFixed</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"結果","isH3":true,"content":"<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Example sample\" id=\"frame_example\" width=\"600\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/web/api/storagemanager/estimate/_sample_.example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://storage.spec.whatwg.org/#site-storage-quota\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Storage<br><small lang=\"ja\">quota の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>初期定義</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"data":null,"query":"api.StorageEstimate.quota","browsers":null}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Storage_API\">Storage API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/StorageManager\"><code>StorageManager</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate\"><code>StorageEstimate</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/StorageManager/estimate_9ffeea37c30a26922d3f1621912db8d8\"><code>StorageEstimate.usage</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"example"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"StorageEstimate ディクショナリの quota プロパティは、StorageManager.estimate() を呼ぶことで得られる、オリジンやウェブアプリに割り当てられているストレージの量の控えめな概算値です。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"ja/conflicting/web/api/storagemanager/estimate_78aa4ffd4dfacc8f94d5c05d150d36ac","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/conflicting/web/api/storagemanager/estimate_78aa4ffd4dfacc8f94d5c05d150d36ac/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"StorageEstimate.quota | MDN","noIndexing":true}}